Website Name - Bhuvan Home
Website URL - https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in/home/index.php
Website Contents - 
This is the home website for Bhuvan , the top bar has access links to 
1)National Resource Sensing Centers Home Website (link for this - https://www.nrsc.gov.in/) , 2)Application Sectors (link for this -https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in/home/index.php#applications_sector) , 3)Bhuvan Collaborators (link for this -https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in/home/collabarators.php) 
4)Search option also called as Bhuvan Data Discovery (https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in/geonetwork/srv/eng/catalog.search#/home)
5)Bhuvan Store which has access to all Bhuvan NOEDA Data Products (https://bhuvan-app1.nrsc.gov.in/2dresources/bhuvanstore.php)
6) Newsletter (https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in/home/newsletter.php)
7) Bhuvan Wiki (https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in/wiki/index.php/Home)

Bhuvan Home Website also provides Latest Updates on Bhuvan and links to Visualisation & Free Download for Collaborative applications 

Also briefly showcases the Application Sectors such as E-Governance , Tourism  , Urban Applications , Urban, Rural Applications, Agriculture , Water , Forestry

Also has links for Maps and OGC (Open Geospatial Consortium) Services that Bhuvan delivers - 
Thematic Services , Ocean Services , Disaster Management Services and Create a map 

this home website also showcases the Bhuvan Central Applications like Central Ministries , Special Applications and G-Goverance Dashboard and State Wise Applications 

Along with these The Home Page also has Statistics of Daily and Monthly Registered Users and Hits in regards to the Bhuvan Geoportal 
